--- Summary ---
At p = 1000003, E has cofactor h = 4 with
prime q = 249727 of 18 bits; no anomalous reduction occurs
at any test prime. At p = 1009 the nontrivial quadratic twist has
h' = 4 with twist prime q' = 251.
